mmy Awards]]===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!| Year\n!| Category\n!| Nominated work\n!| Result\n!| Ref. \n|-\n| [[38th Annual Grammy Awards|1996]] \n| [[Grammy Award for Best Spoken Word Album for Children|Best Spoken Word Album for Children]]\n| ''[[The Diary of a Young Girl]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.grammy.com/grammys/artists/winona-ryder|title= Winona Ruder - Artist|website= Grammys.com|accessdate= April 8, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===[[Screen Actors Guild Awards]]===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!| Year\n!| Nominated work\n!| Category\n!| Result\n!| Ref. \n|-\n| [[2nd Screen Actors Guild Awards|1995]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture|Best Performance by a Cast]]\n| ''[[How to Make an American Quilt]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|rowspan=6|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000213/awards?ref_=nm_awd|title= Winona Ryder - Awards|website= Internet Movie Database|accessdate= April 8, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[17th Screen Actors Guild Awards|2010]]\n|''[[Black Swan (film)|Black Swan]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Female Actor in a Miniseries or Television Movie|Best Actress in a Miniseries or Movie]]\n| ''[[When Love Is Not Enough: The Lois Wilson Story|When Love Is Not Enough]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[24th Screen Actors Guild Awards|2016]]\n|[[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Female Actor in a Drama Series|Best Actress in a Drama]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|''[[Stranger Things]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by an Ensemble in a Drama Series|Best Ensemble in a Drama]]\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[25th Screen Actors Guild Awards|2017]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{sisterlinks|d=Q101797|c=category:Winona Ryder|n=no|b=no|v=no|voy=no|m=no|mw=no|species=no|s=no|wikt=no|q=no}}\n* {{IMDb name|213}}\n* {{Tc